Class ShowGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.ShowGame

  • public class ShowGame
extends java.lang.Object
    The class provide all the functions of showing game detail/progress It determine the showing speed of progress and showing format. It can also determine the speed of the athletes when showing to audiences to control the tension in the game. It also equip with the capability of dealing with accuracy calculation and scaling the competition result of each athletes to make showing smoothly.
    Author:
    Yuan Hao (Alex) Liu s3583320
